Available Tools: set_volume | get_volume | mute | unmute | set_equalizer
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "level": number, "preset": "string" }
Response Schema: { "volume": number, "muted": boolean, "equalizer_preset": "string" }
---
Question: Lower the sound to 20 for the bedtime story session.
Call: { "func_call": "set_volume", "level": 20, "preset": "bedtime" }
Response: { "volume": 20, "muted": false, "equalizer_preset": "bedtime" }

---
Question: Crank the volume up to 95 for the concert livestream.
Call: { "func_call": "set_volume", "level": 95, "preset": "live_event" }
Response: { "volume": 95, "muted": false, "equalizer_preset": "live_event" }

---
Question: Silence the output right now, I have a visitor at the door.
Call: { "func_call": "mute", "level": 55, "preset": "standard" }
Response: { "volume": 55, "muted": true, "equalizer_preset": "standard" }

---
Question: Bring the audio back online and maintain the previous loudness.
Call: { "func_call": "unmute", "level": 55, "preset": "standard" }
Response: { "volume": 55, "muted": false, "equalizer_preset": "standard" }

---
Question: Adjust the level to 40 and enable the electronic music profile.
Call: { "func_call": "set_volume", "level": 40, "preset": "electronic" }
Response: { "volume": 40, "muted": false, "equalizer_preset": "electronic" }

